CADI.Client.Session

Class ClientSessionTargets

  • java.lang.Object
    • CADI.Common.Session.ClientSideSessionTargets
      • CADI.Client.Session.ClientSessionTargets

  • public class ClientSessionTargets
extends ClientSideSessionTargets
    This class implements a list of cached logical targets. Logical targets are cached when a response from a server is sent to a client.

    NOTICE: Methods are not synchronized yet. It may be a problem with the threads.

    Version:
    1.0 2011/10/23
    Author:
    Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)
